{"id":"59e7711e86f7746cae05fbe1","typeName":"Headwear","category":"headwear","parentTypeChain":["Headwear","ArmoredEquipment","Equipment","CompoundItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":"5b47574386f77428ca22b330","price":400},"common":{"name":{"zh":"Kolpak -1S防暴头盔","en":"Kolpak-1S riot helmet"},"shortName":{"zh":"Kolpak","en":"K-1S"},"description":{"zh":"Kolpak-1S可以保护头部免于到冷兵器穿透伤害，符合特殊防护等级GOST R50744-95。它可以抵抗能量50焦耳以上的冲击且避免造成弹片伤害，同时也能减少上述提到的伤害所造成的动载荷。\n\nKolpak-1防护头盔由联盟委员会推荐，供巡逻部队、交通警察、OMON和其他俄罗斯内务部的特殊部队使用。","en":"Kolpak-1S protects the head from the cold piercing-cutting weapons in a special class of protection GOST R50744-95, from fragmentation with an energy of impact up to 50 J, and also serves to reduce the dynamic loads arising from the above-mentioned means of destruction. Kolpak-1 protective helmets are recommended by the Interdepartmental Commission for equipping units of the patrol service, traffic police, OMON and other special units of the Ministry of Internal Affairs of Russia."},"weight":1.9,"width":2,"height":2,"rarity":"Common","backgroundColor":"default"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"ArmorMaterial":"Aramid","ArmorType":"Light","BackgroundColor":"default","BlindnessProtection":0,"BlocksEarpiece":false,"BlocksEyewear":false,"BlocksFaceCover":false,"BlocksHeadwear":false,"BluntThroughput":0.2376,"CanPutIntoDuringTheRaid":true,"CanRequireOnRagfair":false,"CanSellOnRagfair":true,"CantRemoveFromSlotsDuringRaid":[],"ConflictingItems":["5645bcc04bdc2d363b8b4572","5aa2ba71e5b5b000137b758f","5a16b9fffcdbcb0176308b34","66b5f69ea7f72d197e70bcdb","66b5f6a28ca68c6461709ed8","628e4e576d783146b124c64d","66b5f693acff495a294927e3","66b5f6985891c84aab75ca76","5b432b965acfc47a8774094e","66b5f68de98be930d701c00e","6033fa48ffd42c541047f728","5c165d832e2216398b5a7e36","5e4d34ca86f774264f758330","5f60cd6cf2bcbb675b00dac6"],"DeafStrength":"High","Description":"Helmet K1C","DiscardLimit":-1,"DiscardingBlock":false,"DropSoundType":"None","Durability":0,"Ex